  "Title": "OpenClaw: Image Tool `tools.fs.workspaceOnly` Bypass via Sandbox Bridge Mounts",
  "Description": "The `image` tool did not fully honor the `tools.fs.workspaceOnly` filesystem boundary. In affected releases, image-path resolution could still traverse sandbox bridge mounts outside the workspace and read files from mounted directories that the other file tools would reject.",
